patoline (0~20130826) unstable; urgency=low

  * Sync with upstream
  * Update package contents, and add packages for new drivers
  * Package new fonts
  * Fix some lintian warnings (missing extended descriptions,
    and missing Multi-Arch: foreign on architecture independent packages).
  * Generate binary package for vim syntax highlighting.
  * Update trigger which generates META file:
     * bugfix when no ".cmxa" was present in /usr/lib/ocaml/Typography/,
     * and use directives in src/Typography/META generated by configure
       instead of a fixed copy which may be outdated.

